org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication

Class GameEndsMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.Message
      • org.fhnw.aigs.commons.communication.GameEndsMessage

  • public class GameEndsMessage
extends Message
    This message can be sent by the server when the game ends. Usually it will be sent at the end of a Game.checkForWinningCondition()" call. It will inform the clients about the end of the game. There is no built-in logic handling this message - it must be implemented in all clients and games.
